{"tid":1733521,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"請各位關注波台手足青豆雅美","createTime":"2019-11-18T06:20:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-18T12:50:27.000Z","uid":214972,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"61f6d13b8fa501d4d215004195f1c88e5b15f56e","tid":1733521,"uid":214972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:20:01.000Z","msg":"連登會員青豆雅美 <br />\nTg：hugoson1991<br />\n真名：葉XX（估計）<br />\n職業：賣game<br />\n相暫時唔貼住<br />\n<br />\n佢last seen係tg係11/11，之後突然失蹤，但連登一路有上水，但係有d識佢嘅用字唔同咗！<br />\n<br />\n最初我問過佢點解tg唔見人，佢話電話壞咗上唔到tg，連開個一個新tg都無辦法，即係用唔到舊電話，又無新number，但同一時間竟然有其他吹水post波台成員話約咗佢出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢哋竟然可以約一個無電話號碼嘅人出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n我有繼續追查佢下落，但收到一系列不明訊息，全部都係負面字眼，例如監，寃，閹等等，仲有提及isis<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n青豆雅美之前疑似交過d古怪朋友，應該係類似玩藍鯨嗰種，呢方面我已經向其他波台師兄求證，不過佢本人無認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！<br />\n<br />\n我超擔心佢會有乜危險，但報過案又唔受理，而同時有人見我多事都俾咗d威脅性訊息我，但成件事無人提起，因為佢本身唔係同屋企人住，而佢嘅網友都唔覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請各位波台手足關注吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />人命嚟㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />！"},{"pid":"42c668c27a167249125148da8861c40368818489","tid":1733521,"uid":208442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:24:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc1bd4453adb216c58e8d43345cf0233ab565e4a","tid":1733521,"uid":214972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:33:56.000Z","msg":"推1/10"},{"pid":"a1e04118b5c3b72e10cc00327b4a17a657b7d19f","tid":1733521,"uid":214972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-18T06:39:42.000Z","msg":"推2/10"},{"pid":"b1ecd380dd65c63da134721e62ac7c9f37844dcb","tid":1733521,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit